responses.title: From the nether reaches, I return.
This one is in the bag!
On my way to a one-bite kill.
None forget the bite of Viper.
Did you wonder what death was like? Here it is.
You twitch like a snake-bitten mouse.
Your venom was no match for my poison.
Sorry bat, there was something on your back.
First blood, with a poison twist.
I'll take this under my wing.
That gold was weighing me down.
Orb of venom. I need this why?
Now they'll never bring me down.
From the nether reaches, I return.
You can't fight what you can't see.
I am no sorcerer's familiar. Rather, I'll take a sorcerer as my pet.
Who needs legs, when you got wings?
